description:
Nasty Neighbors: No Picnic for Celebrity is an arcade game developed by Orion Games. It was originally released in 2009. GFI published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Skip".
You can play Nasty Neighbors: No Picnic for Celebrity on PC.
